__NAME__ purpose
specify timeout on client sockets
__END__


__NAME__ synopsis
<group choice='plain'>
	<arg choice='plain'><replaceable>time_in_seconds</replaceable></arg>
</group>
__END__


__NAME__ description
The &conf-__FILENAME__; directive specifies the amount of time
&IC; will wait for data on client sockets.
</para><para>
The default is one second, which is the same as the previous
unconfigurable value.
__END__

